    <title>JetBrains许可证申请</title>
    <link href="http://www.x5x5.site/posts/58904/"/>
    <id>http://www.x5x5.site/posts/58904/</id>
    <published>2022-11-21T09:54:48.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-11-22T11:09:05.365Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="免费教育许可证申领"><a href="#免费教育许可证申领" class="headerlink" title="免费教育许可证申领"></a>免费教育许可证申领</h1><h2 id="登录JetBrains官网"><a href="#登录JetBrains官网" class="headerlink" title="登录JetBrains官网"></a>登录JetBrains官网</h2><ul><li><ol><li>点击此处进入官网<a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/zh-cn/community/education/#students">点这里</a></li></ol></li></ul><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211714262.png" alt="image-20221121171445039"></p><ol start="2"><li>按照要求填写完毕(仅限于EDU邮箱)</li></ol><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211716673.png" alt="image-20221121171649603"></p><ol start="3"><li>学信网官方文件</li></ol><p><a href="https://www.chsi.com.cn/">点击链接跳转学信网</a>  登录学信网账号</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211725584.png" alt="image-20221121172507292"></p><p>3.1 然后下载官方文件 ，在点击查看</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211728029.png" alt="image-20221121172815904"></p><p><strong>下载所需要的pdf文件</strong></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211730682.png" alt="image-20221121173048450"></p><p>返回JetBrains申请界面</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211734931.png" alt="image-20221121173425717"></p><ul><li>出现这个界面就等着JB公司给你发消息就可以，一般需要等待15day</li></ul><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211735913.png" alt="image-20221121173524771"></p><p>接收邮件确认列表</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211758796.png" alt="image-20221121175007317"></p><p>在pycharm官网下载 Pycharm-professional 即可免费使用一年</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211750281.png" alt="image-20221121175055192"></p><h3 id="拥有JetBrains许可证"><a href="#拥有JetBrains许可证" class="headerlink" title="拥有JetBrains许可证"></a>拥有JetBrains许可证</h3><ol><li>以下的这些都是JetBrains公司的产品，有兴趣的可以下载使用</li></ol><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wohaoshadiao/image/main/data/202211211752852.png" alt="image-20221121175204779"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
